Forgejo Society: easy-install
=============================

The scripts in this directory (install.sh and install-runner.sh) are a
derivative work of:

    easyforgejo
    https://github.com/wkoszek/easyforgejo
    Copyright (c) Adam Koszek
    Licensed under the MIT License

The substantive changes made for the Forgejo-Society port are:

  - The database backend is PostgreSQL 16 instead of SQLite.
  - A PostgreSQL role and database are created with a randomly
    generated password, written into app.ini, and dropped cleanly on
    purge.
  - The script runs under `set -euo pipefail` and is idempotent
    against re-runs.
  - Hard-coded values are exposed as environment variables (PORT,
    DB_NAME, DB_USER, ADMIN_USER, ADMIN_EMAIL, IP) for overrideability.
  - Banner output, summary block, and accompanying prose follow the
    Forgejo-Society style guide.

